======================================
py-pvt-api
======================================

py-pvt-api provides a set of convenient python bindings
to the Window GigE SDK by Allied Vision Technologies

Requirements:
	You need the PvAPI.dll library.
	(http://www.alliedvisiontec.com/us/products/software/windows/avt-pvapi-sdk.html)

Usage Notes:
	Check the example in example.py.
	Not all functions are implemented, but the example demonstrates
	successful initialization of the camera, captures a frame,
	and then shuts down the driver engine.